  "What is the pH of an acetate buffer with [CH₃COOH] = 0.2 M and [CH₃COO⁻] = 0.1 M? (pKa = 4.74)": "",
  "pH = pKa + log([A⁻]/[HA]) = 4.74 + log(0.1/0.2) = 4.74 + log(0.5) = 4.74 − 0.30 = 4.44.": "",
